Master bedroom is very roomy with walk in closet and grand bathroom with separate garden tub and walk in shower. Huge Teen suite with walk in closet and laundry rounds out the upstairs. Open and flowing floor plan with entertaining friendly main level. Complete with formal dining room and Great Room with real wood burning fireplace. PLEASE CALL OR TEXT NICK GANN 770-715-8842
